column5: Well... I guess you did ok today.
Sweet!   That's one heck of a walleye!!  Congrats!  Oh...the bass were good too. Lol
Wow !! That's a big walleye for sure !!!! Kudos on the release as well !!!! And some real hog bass there too !!!!! Looks like your opening weekend was awesome !!!!! Cheers.  Thanks for sharing
Thanks for the report. Some beauty fish there for sure. You kinda look happy in those pictures.
Fantastic walleye! Nothing wrong with those bass either. Congrats!
Nice eye!  And bass. I guess.  lol  Thanks for the report!
Beauty!  But wait a sec... You're targeting bass and getting a walleye? When I target bass I get pike.What am I doing wrong?

Thanks everyone! I am still completely in shock from the walleye! She was 30 inches, have no idea on a weight,8-10 pounds?  and as for getting walleye bass fishin, this is one of those rare lakes that you can get the walleye flipping trees with texas rigged plastics. Usually there not this big though :0
